\sum Cheeky Wenawon pretends to be dead, to play a trick on his family.
\in A trickster story. Funny story with little likelihood.
\in A man is deemed to be dead by his family, who bury him.  But he is really alive, and plays a trick on his
wife by hiding in another village.  Finally a village celebration brings them back together during the
dances, and it's a happy end.
